replies.body:
People are voluntarily dropping down the ladder. While I, who was stuck in bronze V, am rising because the trolls have gotten their largest desire: To be able to ignore their team.

Bronze V will no longer be the land of low skill and stupid-high ping, but the land of ping muting and giving up at 5. Hey it was already a land of muting from what I could tell. I just carried a 4v5 because our team was communicating while theirs was...well.

{{sticker:slayer-jinx-wink}}
